  "prompt": "How can I retrieve my WeChat account if I've forgotten my password, I just linked my linked & I remember I wechat ID.But I don't have QQ/phone linked?",
  "response": "If you've forgotten your WeChat password and don't have a linked phone number or QQ account, you can try the following steps to recover your account:\n\n1. **Use WeChat ID or Email**:\n   - Open the WeChat app and tap on \u201cLog In\u201d.\n   - Select \u201cForgot Password?\u201d or \u201cCan't Log In?\u201d.\n   - Choose to log in via your WeChat ID or the email linked to your account.\n   - Follow the prompts to reset your password using your WeChat ID or email.\n\n2. **Verify Identity**:\n   - During the password reset process, WeChat may prompt you to verify your identity. Follow the instructions provided to complete this verification. This may include answering security questions or providing additional information.\n\n3. **Seek Help from Friends**:\n   - If you're unable to reset your password via WeChat ID or email, you may be asked to verify your identity through WeChat contacts. WeChat might allow you to request verification from friends who can vouch for your identity.\n\n4. **Use the WeChat Help Center**:\n   - Visit the WeChat Help Center or their official website.\n   - Look for options related to account recovery or password issues.\n   - Follow the instructions for account recovery, which might include submitting a support request.\n\n5. **Contact WeChat Support**:\n   - If none of the above methods work, reach out to WeChat support for assistance. You can do this by finding the contact information for WeChat support online or within the app's help section. Be prepared to provide detailed information about your account to verify your identity.\n\n6. **Check for Other Linked Accounts**:\n   - Even if you believe no other accounts are linked, double-check for any backup email or platforms you might have used when you first registered.\n\nRemember, the available recovery options may vary based on your account's settings and your region, so it's important to follow the specific guidance provided by WeChat during the recovery process.",
